  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2007-06-11",
    "date": "2007-06-29T15:43:54Z",
    "text": "Calls for government leaders and law enforcement personnel to ensure that the civil rights and civil liberties of all Americans, including Iranian-Americans, are fully protected.\n\nCondemns bigotry and acts of violence or discrimination against any American.\n\nEncourages Iranian-Americans to share with their elected officials and their community incidences of discrimination in an effort to end stereotypes, correct misconceptions, and convey instances of abuse.\n\nCalls upon law enforcement authorities to vigorously investigate and prosecute crimes that are based on actual or perceived, race, color, religion, national origin, or ethnicity."
  },
